         <head>THE TUFT OF KELP.</head>
         <lg>
            <l>ALL dripping in tangles green,</l>
            <l rend="indent">Cast up by a lonely sea,</l>
            <l rend="indent2">If purer for that, O Weed,</l>
            <l rend="indent3">Bitterer, too, are ye ?</l>
         </lg>
      </body>
